modName: Shadow Force  Armor UNP or UUNP Bodyslide HDT - DELETED
summary:
Based on the original blunt outfit of the classic game Shadow Force.
Production can be made from blacksmith's other items and the colored clothing is in Sky Blue, Pink, Red.
Thank you to the people who helped us build it.
I'm not a mode maker. I was helped by moders to make it. I don't want there to be any misunderstanding.
